Besides rodents

06:19.648 --> 06:20.959
and my favorite

06:18.334 --> 06:20.959
pair of slippers.

06:21.000 --> 06:22.271
I know you ate them,

06:22.272 --> 06:23.542
you've been pooping lint!

06:23.584 --> 06:24.709
(GROWLS)

06:25.667 --> 06:27.230
Oh, I get it.

06:27.231 --> 06:28.792
You miss Ravi.

06:28.834 --> 06:31.167
Well, he misses you too.

06:31.209 --> 06:32.268
- You know
- what I'm missing?

06:32.292 --> 06:34.250
- My favorite
- sci-fi opera show,

06:34.292 --> 06:35.125
Aria 51.

06:35.167 --> 06:36.167
(LAUGHS)

06:37.125 --> 06:38.250
Gimme that!

06:40.209 --> 06:41.334
(BELCHES)

06:41.375 --> 06:44.000
You ate my remote control!

06:44.042 --> 06:45.167
If I ate something

06:45.168 --> 06:46.292
every time I was upset...

06:46.334 --> 06:47.375
(MRS. KIPLING SNARLS)

06:47.417 --> 06:49.042
Okay, I'm a bad example.

06:51.250 --> 06:52.667
- You might have
- hypothermia.

06:52.709 --> 06:53.918
Let me warm you up.

06:55.459 --> 06:57.043
Here, have

06:57.044 --> 06:58.626
soup instead.

06:58.667 --> 06:59.980
It's a lot warmer,

06:59.981 --> 07:01.292
and it won't watch you

06:58.667 --> 07:01.292
while you sleep.

07:03.000 --> 07:04.063
So, what were you doing

07:04.064 --> 07:05.125
all alone in the ocean?

07:05.167 --> 07:07.000
Actually...

07:07.042 --> 07:08.417
I don't know.

07:08.459 --> 07:09.543
I have this

07:09.544 --> 07:10.626
terrible headache,

07:10.667 --> 07:11.897
and I can't seem

07:11.898 --> 07:13.125
to remember anything.

07:13.167 --> 07:15.250
(GASPS) Oh, my gosh,

07:15.292 --> 07:16.626
she has amnesty!

07:19.000 --> 07:20.293
The word

07:20.294 --> 07:21.584
is "amnesia."

07:21.626 --> 07:22.918
How did she get

07:22.919 --> 07:24.209
out of middle school?

07:24.250 --> 07:26.167
- The system
- is broken.

07:27.834 --> 07:29.667
- Wait. So, you don't
- remember anything?

07:29.709 --> 07:32.542
It's all pretty fuzzy,

07:32.543 --> 07:35.375
but I kind of remember

07:29.709 --> 07:35.375
singing.

07:35.417 --> 07:36.876
And for some reason,

07:36.877 --> 07:38.334
the word "Delphina."

07:38.375 --> 07:40.042
- That must
- be your name!

07:40.083 --> 07:41.375
Delphina Ross.

07:43.375 --> 07:45.167
- Jessie,
- can we keep her?

07:45.209 --> 07:46.730
Please, please,

07:46.731 --> 07:48.250
please, please,

07:45.209 --> 07:48.250
please?

