Don't ask us.

07:57.752 --> 07:59.125
We round to

07:56.375 --> 07:59.125
the nearest thousand.

08:01.209 --> 08:02.292
Okay, we should

08:02.293 --> 08:03.375
let you get some rest.

08:03.417 --> 08:04.778
- I'll show you
- to the stateroom.

08:05.417 --> 08:06.334
(GASPS)

08:06.375 --> 08:07.792
Whoops!

08:07.834 --> 08:09.476
- It's like I don't know
- how to work my legs.

08:09.500 --> 08:10.751
JESSIE: Ah...

08:10.792 --> 08:12.310
- Been there. - After my first
- Spin class,

08:12.334 --> 08:13.626
- I couldn't walk
- for a week.

08:16.250 --> 08:18.667
Guys, I figured it out!

08:18.709 --> 08:20.459
Swims in the ocean,

08:20.500 --> 08:21.730
wears a shell bra

08:21.731 --> 08:22.959
and seaweed,

08:23.000 --> 08:24.105
doesn't know how

08:24.106 --> 08:25.209
to work her legs...

08:25.250 --> 08:27.042
- Don't you see
- what Delphina is?

08:27.083 --> 08:28.209
A clumsy

08:28.210 --> 08:29.334
shell collector with

08:27.083 --> 08:29.334
no fashion sense?

08:30.667 --> 08:34.208
No! She's a mermaid!

08:34.250 --> 08:35.480
I'm pretty sure

08:35.481 --> 08:36.708
we can still get

08:34.250 --> 08:36.708
married in California.

