Okay, Delphina

08:42.376 --> 08:43.376
is lying down.

08:43.417 --> 08:44.730
I hope you tucked

08:44.731 --> 08:46.042
her in with a wet towel.

08:46.083 --> 08:47.375
We gotta keep her moist!

08:47.417 --> 08:49.375
Why? She's not a meatloaf.

08:50.459 --> 08:51.647
I know.

08:51.648 --> 08:52.834
She's a mermaid!

08:52.876 --> 08:53.960
I told you we'd

08:53.961 --> 08:55.042
find one out here!

08:55.083 --> 08:56.209
Zuri, Delphina

08:56.210 --> 08:57.334
is not a mermaid.

08:57.375 --> 08:59.042
- And please
- don't tell her she is.

08:59.083 --> 09:00.685
- The poor kid's already
- confused enough.

09:00.709 --> 09:01.814
I know a mermaid

09:01.815 --> 09:02.918
when I see one!

09:02.959 --> 09:05.042
Okay, Ravi, back me up.

09:05.083 --> 09:06.772
Actually, more than 95%

09:06.773 --> 09:08.459
of the ocean is unexplored.

09:08.500 --> 09:10.375
- New species are
- discovered every day.

09:10.417 --> 09:11.896
So a mermaid is not

09:11.897 --> 09:13.375
altogether implausible.

09:13.417 --> 09:14.876
See? Smarty McScience

09:14.877 --> 09:16.334
over here agrees with me!

09:18.083 --> 09:19.355
I have so many

09:19.356 --> 09:20.626
questions for Delphina.

09:20.667 --> 09:21.876
- I'm gonna go
- get my list!

09:23.459 --> 09:24.584
Thanks. You're about

09:24.585 --> 09:25.709
