- At the time?

22:32.542 --> 22:34.375
Ah, yes.

22:34.417 --> 22:35.730
That would explain why

22:35.731 --> 22:37.042
she also tested positive

22:37.083 --> 22:38.355
for tartar sauce

22:38.356 --> 22:39.626
and a squeeze of lemon.

22:46.876 --> 22:50.000
Whoa! Best vacation ever!

22:54.417 --> 22:56.126
Hey, how about you put

22:56.127 --> 22:57.834
