(SIGHS)

23:02.709 --> 23:03.709
(YELPS) Ravi!

23:06.083 --> 23:07.250
What are you doing?

23:07.292 --> 23:08.876
You said,

23:08.918 --> 23:10.459
"Hey, how about you

23:10.460 --> 23:12.000
put a little sunscreen

23:08.918 --> 23:12.000
on me, hot stuff?"

